* :QhexXoP3ZxHB6DZS: A window can be split horizontally with `C-x 2`, or vertically with `C-x 3`. That can be repeated. To make the current window occupy the entire frame, use `C-x 1`. To switch between windows in a frame, use `C-x o`, or in move-submode, simply `o`.
